data.description: This charming home is ideal for first time home buyers! This immaculate home features an open floor plan, laminate flooring, and new appliances, updated kitchen with dining nook, a spacious family room with fireplace, a large one car garage, spacious back yard perfect for entertaining or pets, and large side yard big enough for boat/rv storage. Spacious floorplan with large rooms, newer HVAC, newer roof, updated plumbing. Completely turnkey and ready for move-in! It is conveniently located near the freeway & schools. Close to parks and schools.  This home features a beautifully updated kitchen with quartz counter-tops, new cabinets & stainless steel appliances. New installed windows. Fresh interior/exterior paint. Tiled bathroom floor & shower. Come & see it! It is priced, right!
